---
title: Oven-Baked Salmon with Black Garlic Sauce, Veggies and Roasted Potatoes
description: We love good Oven-Baked Salmon & Black Garlic Sauce and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oven-baked-salmon-ef26451e-513c2e7d.jpg
